cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with pose estimation from depth images using CNNs. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed algorithm is applicable to Human Robot Interaction scenarios. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as CNNs are a popular tool in AI research. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new network architecture for body landmark localization. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the dataset used in the paper includes synthetic images of human bodies.
